# Vitest snapshot files — we don't commit these.
# Calc definition snapshots were 60K lines of duplicated i18n + Zod
# internals; library upgrades churned all of them with zero semantic
# change. Snapshot.test.ts files now use assertDefinitionShape() from
# @/test-utils which gives the same coverage via property assertions.
**/__snapshots__/
**/__snapshots__/*.snap
*.snap
